# =========================================================
# Codespaces-specific .env.local template
# Project: resurgence-designxpress-biz
# =========================================================
#
# How to use
# 1) Keep this file local inside your GitHub Codespace.
# 2) Do NOT commit real values.
# 3) For secrets, either:
#    - paste the actual values directly below, or
#    - replace with values exported from Codespaces secrets in your shell/session.
#
# Suggested split
# - Secrets: server-only, credentials, tokens, keys, passwords
# - Safe local vars: public-facing config and non-sensitive metadata
#
# Notes
# - NEXT_PUBLIC_* variables are exposed to the browser by Next.js.
# - Values shown as blank should be filled from Vercel.

# =========================================================
# SECRETS
# =========================================================

